Package: bootstrapper
Title: Opinionated R Package Quickstart
Version: 1.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Visruth", "Srimath Kandali", , "public@visruth.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-9097-0688"))
Description: Bootstrap new R packages with strongly opinionated defaults.
    Creates the package scaffold, wires up tests, README and NEWS,
    configures GitHub Actions and Dependabot, adds Air/Jarl setup, and
    drop in a default AGENTS.md for building R packages.
